Description

Latest Gujarat Government Jobs for Graduates in various fields have been published by Gujarat Public Service Commission for Dy. Section Officer vacancies in Gujarat. If you are searching for a government job in Gujarat then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for the vacancies of Dy. Section Officer, from 05-06-2021, and till 11-06-2021. If you are interested in all these vacancies in Gujarat and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.

Application fee

  • Mode of application is Online

Important dates

  •  The starting date to apply in these posts is 05-06-2021.
  •  Last date to apply in these posts is 11-06-2021
  • Date for Prelims Exam Date for Advt No 139/2020-21: 08-08-2021
  • Date for Mains Exam Date for Advt No 139/2020-21: 14 & 21-11-2021

Age Limit Criteria

  • For General Candidate, you should be between 21 to 37  years old. 

Detailed Vacancies:

GPSC Dy. Section Officer Pay Scale

  • According to the information given by the Gujarat Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is 39600-126600 /-.

How to apply for GPSC Dy. Section Officer Recruitment 2021?

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process of the Dy. Section Officer. Fill in your details and submit it or follow all the steps given below.

  •  First, go to the official website of GPSC and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked by GPSC.
  • Then save it and complete the application submission.
  • Then to fully complete the process you have to submit the application fee.
  • And finally, download the application form for future purposes.
